definition: Jiangbei district of central Chongqing municipality, formerly in Sichuan/Chongqing's main airport/Jiangbei district of Ningbo city 寧波市|宁波市[Ning2 bo1 shi4], Zhejiang

sentences.english: When applied at a few inspection points in Jiangbei District of Chongqing, this method proved to be feasible.
